err_message.en: Project ID [{{projectId}}] is not valid. The project ID must be 3-63 characters long, contains only lowercase letters, numbers, dot(.) and hyphen (-), begins and ends with the letters or numbers (except “xn”). The ID must be unique and not in IP address format.
err_message.cn: 无效的项目编号 [{{projectId}}]。 项目编号必须为3-63个字符，只包括小写字母、数字、点（.）以及连字号（-），必须以字母或者数字开头和结尾（除了xn开头之外）。项目编号必须是唯一的，并且不能是IP地址格式。

err_message.en: Xcalbuild execution failed, but .i file is generated.
err_message.cn: Xcalbuild执行失败，但.i文件已经生成。

err_message.en: Xcalbuild success but no .i file is generated. Probably due to project not cleaned before first scan/ no source code in the project/ source code is same as previous scan.
err_message.cn: Xcalbuild成功，但是没有生成.i文件。可能是由于项目在第一次扫描前没有被清理/项目中没有源代码/源代码与之前的扫描相同。

err_message.en: Xcalbuild execution failed, no .i file is generated.
err_message.cn: Xcalbuild执行失败，没有生成.i文件。

err_message.en: Build itself is part of the scan process. Please fix the build or the make file. Otherwise, no issue will be reported.
err_message.cn: 扫描准备失败，无法生成源代码预编译文件

err_message.en: Build error. No i file generated.
err_message.cn: 扫描准备失败，可能与用户自己的Makefile设置有关

err_message.en: Please trigger the scan via push or merge. Otherwise, no DSR will be reported.
err_message.cn: 前一次扫描含有dsr结果，无法获取commit id 或者baseline commit id, 退出

err_message.en: Scan preparation failed. Unable to upload file to file service.
err_message.cn: 扫描准备失败，无法上传文件到文件服务器

err_message.en: Cannot access file service, please check whether the file service url or network is valid. You can also contact your administrator.
err_message.cn: 无法访问文件服务，请检查文件服务地址或者网络是否是有效的。你也可以联系系统管理员。

err_message.en: [CICD] Your scan config file is corrupted, please restore previous correct config file.
err_message.cn: [CICD] 您的扫描配置文件已损坏，请使用之前正确的配置文件。

err_message.en: [CICD] There is an invalid input for the “repoAction”. Please ensure the value is “CI”, “CD” or “TRIAL”.
err_message.cn: [CICD] 输入了无效的“repoAction“值。允许输入值的范围为“CI/CD/TRIAL“。

err_message.en: [CICD] Inconsistent input for “repoAction”, please start from scratch.
err_message.cn: [CICD] 输入了不一致的“repoAction“值。请重新创建项目。

err_message.en: [CICD] The “repoAction” has already been set as the “CI” and cannot be changed to “CD”. Please refer to the User Manual to set up a new “CD” scan pipeline.
err_message.cn: [CICD] 在扫描配置文件中，“repoAction”之前的值设定为“CI“，不能更改为“CD“。如果您想要创建“CD“扫描流程，请参阅用户手册（注意：此操作将会创建新的CICD扫描流程）。

err_message.en: [Config] Revise the error message for the said case to Scan mode was found different from the original. Please create a new project for a different scan mode.
err_message.cn: [Config] 扫描模式与原来的不同。请为不同的扫描模式创建一个新项目。

err_message.en: Prepare bucket in file service failed, please contact your administrator.
err_message.cn: 在文件服务中准备桶失败，请联系系统管理员。

err_message.en: [Project] The Project ID cannot be found or created. Please make sure the project ID is correct. Please try again or contact your system administrator if the problem persists.
err_message.cn: [Project] 无法找到或创建项目ID。请确认项目ID是正确的并重试。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。

err_message.en: [CICD] The “repoAction” has already been set as the “CD” and cannot be changed to “CI”. Please create a new scan configuration file for CI scan pipeline.
err_message.cn: [CICD] 在扫描配置文件中，“repoAction”之前的值设定为“CD“，不能更改为“CI“。请为CI重新创建扫描配置文件。

err_message.en: Duplicate roject name [{{projectName}}], please use a different project name.
err_message.cn: Duplicate roject name [{{projectName}}], please use a different project name.
